      "content": "\"let go and stop trying\"... what does that even mean? like, are you saying i should just stop fighting it? because i'm so tired of fighting. sometimes i just wish i could find some kind of actual peace, like just... not having to deal with any of this anymore. is that even a thing you can find?",
